---
title: Spiced Moroccan Soup with Lentils & Chickpeas
description: They say 'you can lead a camel to water but you can’t make him drink'. We’re pretty sure if you led him to this steaming bowl of Moroccan soup, you wouldn’t have a problem! This recipe is inspired by the Head Chef recent trip to the Atlas Mountains where he spent time with the nomadic Berbers.
